### Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/api/health

### Get Products
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products

### Create Order with PayMe QR
POST http://localhost:4000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "1",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": "4",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "customerName": "Chan Tai Man",
  "customerPhone": "91234567",
  "customerEmail": "chan@example.com",
  "shippingAddress": {
    "street": "123 Main Street",
    "district": "Central",
    "city": "Hong Kong"
  }
}

### Get Order Status
GET http://localhost:4000/api/orders/ORD123456

### Admin: List All Orders
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/orders

### Admin: Update Order Status
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/admin/orders/ORD123456/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "paid"
}